# CUSTOM rules start here
# Unblock traffic which originates from 9Anime and isn't blocked for being malicious as seen below.
@@||*^$domain=9anime.to|9anime.ru|9anime.live|9anime.nl|9anime.one|9anime.love|9anime.life|9anime.tv|9anime.page|9anime.video